{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, it is worth noting that data wrangling still require human involvement, especially in complex scenarios.",
    "One potential avenue would be to integrate agent-assisted data annotation and cleaning into LightVA's workflow.",
    "In addition, there may be a lack of finesse and aesthetic appeal in interface visualizations and interactions when compared to manual designs.",
    "Despite this, the overall cost-effectiveness has been enhanced.",
    "To address this concern, we offer support for exporting the code, which can be further modified as needed."
  ]
}